OL,3,CPlans to ban single-use plastic bags
OL,4,Cput on hold
OL,6,FPlans to ban single-use plastic bags
OL,7,Fand polystyrene takeaway containers in
OL,8,FWales have been put on hold.
OL,10,FThe Welsh Government wanted to ban the
OL,11,Fuse of these items by the spring.
OL,12,FHowever, it now says it is no longer
OL,13,Fviable to agree these changes with the
OL,14,FUK Government in time.
OL,16,FItems including straws, cutlery,
OL,17,Fcotton buds and single-use vapes are
OL,18,Falready banned in Wales under the
OL,19,FEnvironmental Protection (Single-use
OL,20,FPlastic Products) (Wales) Act 2023.
