OL,3,CPlans to ban single-use plastic bags
OL,4,Cput on hold
OL,6,FFrom 18 December 2026, the Single-use
OL,7,FPlastic Products Act will also
OL,8,Frestrict the supply of wet wipes
OL,9,Fcontaining plastic.
OL,11,FThe plans have been shelved due to
OL,12,Fcomplications with the UK Internal
OL,13,FMarket Act, which states that goods
OL,14,Fmust be able to be sold across the UK.
