OL,3,CPlans to ban single-use plastic bags
OL,4,Cput on hold
OL,6,FCabinet Secretary for Climate Change
OL,7,Fand Rural Affairs, Huw Irranca-Davies
OL,8,Fsaid: "We remain committed to seeing
OL,9,Fpolystyrene lids for cups or takeaway
OL,10,Ffood containers, plastic single-use
OL,11,Fcarrier bags or products made of oxo-
OL,12,Fdegradable plastic banned and are
OL,13,Fworking to achieve that as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible."
OL,16,F"By phasing out unnecessary singleuse
OL,17,Fproducts...we are delivering our
OL,18,Fambition to end the throwaway culture,
OL,19,Fcreating a more sustainable Wales, one
OL,20,Fwe are proud to hand on to future
OL,21,Fgenerations."
